name: Demo Flight
location_str: Long March 12A Pad @ Jiuquan Satellite Launch Center, CHN
description: First test launch of CASC/SAST’s Long March 12A rocket, with a dummy payload. The rocket’s 1st stage attempted to land on a landing pad about 300 km downrange of the launch site.
rocket_fact: The 'Max-Q' callout during launch refers to the moment of maximum dynamic pressure, where structural stress on the vehicle is highest.
